{"tid":1068262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[外國港鐵] F22墜毀美軍方：訓練啫","createTime":"2019-03-19T06:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T14:48:24.000Z","uid":107362,"like":80,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"fdd1dcf6a2a45b6795c016723849f6a549406a7f","tid":1068262,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNtNkcn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNtNkcn.png&h=673929b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傳媒拍攝到有不明物體在F22機腹。<br />\n<br />\n近日港鐵系統測試故障，導致兩列車嚴重損毀，中環站至金鐘站服務暫停近兩日。地鐵列車相撞為四十年一遇，箇中原因當然引人入勝。但港鐵至今只肯透露意外因測試系統所致。<br />\n<br />\n其實大型機構甚或政府向公眾隱瞞真相，已非新鮮。早在2008年，美軍兩架F22離奇墜毀，空軍上校洛克卻透露只是為預先安排的訓練，兩名機師皆無大礙。但有傳媒卻得到美軍中人發放內幕照片，F22墜毀的真正原因竟然是受到不明物體襲擊！<br />\n<br />\n圖中清楚看見有不明物體在F22機腹。如此震撼的消息，政府竟然支吾以對，看來今次港鐵有史以來最嚴重的事故，其原因肯定不簡單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/19/134816_ab961cdf8fef66895761a8618bed675b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F19%2F134816_ab961cdf8fef66895761a8618bed675b.png&h=bab9cedb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國空軍上校洛克。"},{"pid":"99b86a7092d64bc224d60f3a32411c168602dff5","tid":1068262,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:04:00.000Z","msg":"好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fba18f5513f3c8c259284138fcf3ca3766a3b64","tid":1068262,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9634bbbfde5a0d6bd720cb5ff7669de29c1ce378","tid":1068262,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"99b86a7092d64bc224d60f3a32411c168602dff5","tid":1068262,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T06:04:00.000Z","msg":"好好笑<img